<span begin="23.949" end="24.072">ど</span><span begin="24.072" end="24.192">う</span><span begin="24.192" end="24.330">も</span><span begin="24.330" end="24.699">暑</span><span begin="24.699" end="24.888">い</span><span begin="24.888" end="25.140">か</span><span begin="25.140" end="25.605">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">近来实在是燥热难耐</span></p><p begin="27.053" end="29.481" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="27.053" end="27.174">た</span><span begin="27.174" end="27.302">だ</span><span begin="27.302" end="27.554">風</span><span begin="27.554" end="27.768">が</span><span begin="27.768" end="27.903">吹</span><span begin="27.903" end="28.027">く</span><span begin="28.027" end="28.157">の</span><span begin="28.157" end="28.274">を</span><span begin="28.274" end="28.753">待</span><span begin="28.753" end="28.975">って</span><span begin="28.975" end="29.481">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只是静候着一缕清风</span></p><p begin="30.900" end="33.224" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="30.900" end="31.123">木</span><span begin="31.123" end="31.899">陰</span><span begin="31.899" end="32.195">に</span><span begin="32.195" end="32.828">座</span><span begin="32.828" end="33.224">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">坐在树荫下</span></p><p begin="34.768" end="36.911" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="34.768" end="35.440">何</span><span begin="35.440" end="35.566">か</span><span begin="35.566" end="36.172">頬</span><span begin="36.172" end="36.386">に</span><span begin="36.386" end="36.644">付</span><span begin="36.644" end="36.911">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">有什么东西粘上了脸颊</span></p><p begin="38.573" end="43.204" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="38.573" end="38.838">見</span><span begin="38.838" end="39.304">上</span><span begin="39.304" end="39.554">げ</span><span begin="39.554" end="39.943">れ</span><span begin="39.943" end="40.204">ば</span><span begin="40.204" end="40.446">頭</span><span begin="40.446" end="41.202">上</span><span begin="41.202" end="41.499">に</span><span begin="41.499" end="41.708">咲</span><span begin="41.708" end="41.936">い</span><span begin="41.936" end="42.124">て</span><span begin="42.124" end="42.425">散</span><span begin="42.425" end="43.204">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">向上望去，头顶一片花开花落</span></p><p begin="45.758" end="49.644" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="45.758" end="46.018">は</span><span begin="46.018" end="46.266">ら</span><span begin="46.266" end="46.493">り、</span><span begin="46.493" end="46.994">僕</span><span begin="46.994" end="47.335">ら</span><span begin="47.335" end="47.531">も</span><span begin="47.531" end="47.725">う</span><span begin="47.949" end="48.428">息</span><span begin="48.428" end="48.632">も</span><span begin="48.632" end="49.169">忘</span><span begin="49.169" end="49.385">れ</span><span begin="49.385" end="49.644">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">飞花飘零，我们连呼吸也忘却</span></p><p begin="49.889" end="53.461" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="49.889" end="50.805">瞬</span><span begin="50.805" end="51.142">き</span><span begin="51.142" end="51.334">さ</span><span begin="51.334" end="51.491">え</span><span begin="51.491" end="52.019">億</span><span begin="52.019" end="53.461">劫</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">甚至不愿眨眼</span></p><p begin="53.644" end="57.490" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="53.644" end="53.844">さ</span><span begin="53.844" end="54.159">ぁ、</span><span begin="54.159" end="54.381">今</span><span begin="54.381" end="54.633">日</span><span begin="54.633" end="54.904">さ</span><span begin="54.904" end="55.151">え</span><span begin="55.151" end="55.373">明</span><span begin="55.373" end="55.845">日</span><span begin="55.845" end="56.078">過</span><span begin="56.078" end="56.363">去</span><span begin="56.363" end="56.582">に</span><span begin="56.582" end="56.796">変</span><span begin="56.796" end="57.027">わ</span><span begin="57.027" end="57.490">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">看吧，就连今天到了明日也将变成过去</span></p><p begin="57.770" end="1:00.863" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="57.770" end="57.997">た</span><span begin="57.997" end="58.476">だ</span><span begin="58.476" end="59.252">風</span><span begin="59.252" end="59.457">を</span><span begin="59.457" end="59.680">待</span><span begin="59.680" end="1:00.863">つ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只是静候春风</span></p><p begin="1:01.141" end="1:05.062" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:01.141" end="1:01.384">だ</span><span begin="1:01.384" end="1:01.624">か</span><span begin="1:01.624" end="1:01.838">ら</span><span begin="1:01.838" end="1:02.359">僕</span><span begin="1:02.359" end="1:02.683">ら</span><span begin="1:02.683" end="1:02.888">も</span><span begin="1:02.888" end="1:03.078">う</span><span begin="1:03.304" end="1:03.771">声</span><span begin="1:03.771" end="1:04.025">も</span><span begin="1:04.025" end="1:04.517">忘</span><span begin="1:04.517" end="1:04.754">れ</span><span begin="1:04.754" end="1:05.062">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">所以我们连声音也忘却</span></p><p begin="1:05.175" end="1:08.826" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:05.175" end="1:05.423">さ</span><span begin="1:05.423" end="1:05.692">よ</span><span begin="1:05.692" end="1:06.184">な</span><span begin="1:06.184" end="1:06.456">ら</span><span begin="1:06.456" end="1:06.648">さ</span><span begin="1:06.648" end="1:06.847">え</span><span begin="1:06.847" end="1:07.380">億</span><span begin="1:07.380" end="1:08.826">劫</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">甚至不愿说出再见</span></p><p begin="1:09.068" end="1:13.714" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:09.068" end="1:09.299">た</span><span begin="1:09.299" end="1:09.514">だ</span><span begin="1:09.514" end="1:10.015">花</span><span begin="1:10.015" end="1:10.252">が</span><span begin="1:10.252" end="1:10.742">降</span><span begin="1:10.742" end="1:10.983">る</span><span begin="1:10.983" end="1:11.220">だ</span><span begin="1:11.220" end="1:12.197">け</span><span begin="1:12.888" end="1:13.138">晴</span><span begin="1:13.138" end="1:13.382">れ</span><span begin="1:13.382" end="1:13.714">り</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只是落花纷纷</span></p><p begin="1:13.857" end="1:16.756" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:13.857" end="1:14.580">今、</span><span begin="1:14.580" end="1:15.054">春</span><span begin="1:15.054" end="1:15.528">吹</span><span begin="1:15.528" end="1:16.756">雪</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">此刻，阳光明媚，樱飞漫天</span></p><p begin="1:32.596" end="1:34.651" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:32.596" end="1:32.766">次</span><span begin="1:32.766" end="1:32.927">の</span><span begin="1:32.927" end="1:33.089">日</span><span begin="1:33.089" end="1:33.304">も</span><span begin="1:33.304" end="1:33.557">待</span><span begin="1:33.557" end="1:33.807">ち</span><span begin="1:33.807" end="1:34.041">合</span><span begin="1:34.041" end="1:34.262">わ</span><span begin="1:34.262" end="1:34.651">せ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">第二天也是碰头的日子</span></p><p begin="1:36.432" end="1:39.101" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:36.432" end="1:36.648">花</span><span begin="1:36.648" end="1:36.803">見</span><span begin="1:36.803" end="1:36.926">の</span><span begin="1:36.926" end="1:37.094">客</span><span begin="1:37.094" end="1:37.250">も</span><span begin="1:37.250" end="1:37.614">少</span><span begin="1:37.614" end="1:37.869">な</span><span begin="1:37.869" end="1:38.105">く</span><span begin="1:38.105" end="1:38.590">な</span><span begin="1:38.590" end="1:39.101">った</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">来赏花的游客也变少了</span></p><p begin="1:40.286" end="1:42.432" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:40.286" end="1:40.521">春</span><span begin="1:40.521" end="1:40.681">の</span><span begin="1:40.681" end="1:40.911">匂</span><span begin="1:40.911" end="1:41.024">い</span><span begin="1:41.024" end="1:41.257">は</span><span begin="1:41.257" end="1:41.474">も</span><span begin="1:41.474" end="1:41.716">う</span><span begin="1:41.716" end="1:41.953">止</span><span begin="1:41.953" end="1:42.432">む</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">春日的气息已然画上句点</span></p><p begin="1:44.093" end="1:46.250" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:44.093" end="1:44.210">今</span><span begin="1:44.210" end="1:44.443">年</span><span begin="1:44.443" end="1:44.602">も</span><span begin="1:44.602" end="1:44.843">夏</span><span begin="1:44.843" end="1:45.069">が</span><span begin="1:45.069" end="1:45.275">来</span><span begin="1:45.275" end="1:45.547">る</span><span begin="1:45.547" end="1:45.763">の</span><span begin="1:45.763" end="1:46.250">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">今年也要迎来夏天了吗？</span></p><p begin="1:47.987" end="1:50.145" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:47.987" end="1:48.183">高</span><span begin="1:48.183" end="1:48.306">架</span><span begin="1:48.306" end="1:48.721">橋</span><span begin="1:48.721" end="1:48.932">を</span><span begin="1:48.932" end="1:49.143">抜</span><span begin="1:49.143" end="1:49.380">け</span><span begin="1:49.380" end="1:49.639">た</span><span begin="1:49.639" end="1:50.145">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">穿过高架桥</span></p><p begin="1:51.809" end="1:54.231" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:51.809" end="1:51.956">道</span><span begin="1:51.956" end="1:52.075">の</span><span begin="1:52.075" end="1:52.461">先</span><span begin="1:52.461" end="1:52.608">に</span><span begin="1:52.608" end="1:52.983">君</span><span begin="1:52.983" end="1:53.237">が</span><span begin="1:53.237" end="1:53.634">覗</span><span begin="1:53.634" end="1:53.923">い</span><span begin="1:53.923" end="1:54.231">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在道路的前方瞥见了你的身影</span></p><p begin="1:55.605" end="1:57.819" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v